- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the application of RM-Polar codes in network communication. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also possible for similar reasons as cs.SI. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss the algorithmic aspects of constructing RM-Polar codes.
